room_title: Escape room "When Alice Fell" by Sleuth Escape Rooms in Kearney
room_description:
The Queen of Hearts has lost her tarts, her crown....and her MIND!

Between the incessant ticking of the clocks and the crazy riddles found there, the Queen demands her crown be found, or HEADS WILL ROLL!

Take a leap into the Rabbit hole and find the crown before Wonderland is lost - FOREVER!
